        <p>We are delighted to work with Disability Snowsport UK (DSUK) and Save The Planet Academy via a donation from each guest booking. We also partner with Scotland: The Big Picture through the sponsorship of local projects. Our team actively raise funds throughout the year, by taking part in challenges and events.</p>
